Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說過世間萬物都有著靈魂 這樣的說法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論什麼 只要被珍惜的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見習神仙愛心蛋 就會從中誕生哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是秘密事項喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『去找吧！蛋仙人』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有通過這艱苦的修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能成為獨當一面的（街頭霸王？）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢於面對艱苦修煉的這份青春
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好的學學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我們也為了成長起來 正在修煉中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫忘了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 當我們獨當一面的時候 會變得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到是只知道會成為很了不起的大神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 電視壞掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 這種時候 只用從這角度敲下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣怎麼可能修好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時就交給電視機的神仙 由我來...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老朽是偉大的仙人愛心蛋 名曰蛋仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙...仙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人就是在遠離世俗之處進行著各種修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,習得渾身法力的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不明白你在說什麼 但好像很厲害的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的大人物 找我們有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見習愛心蛋們 好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找到老朽的話 就給你們很棒的獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！ 獎勵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期限在明天日落之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是找到他 連長什麼樣都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請給我更多的試煉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是仙人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好在意獎勵是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是很好吃的零食～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何 都絕對要找出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家齊心協力 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在玩什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說啊 剛才發生了不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我說的 現在一定要找到蛋仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上出發吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不行的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太激動了 晚上肯定睡不著啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 明天再說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我關燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外出還真不錯 但是要從哪找起呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人的話 給人一種會住在高處的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒 先找高樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那裡有高高的大廈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直達觀景層的電梯 維修中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電梯壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬樓梯不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！爬上去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
