Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 加油 心彩～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 加油 心彩～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 加油 心彩～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 加油 心彩～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終... 終於到了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 來找仙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 有在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在這裡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他比較高的地方 只有學校的後山了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫著『』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 加油 心彩～ X 2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著去哪找？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人都是住在桃源鄉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃源鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多桃子的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就去 馬上就去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是『』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 『』？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是桃園喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然現在還沒結果子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次畫了個圓？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 這圓就是句號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把之前找到的字連起來讀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能得到提示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提示？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 蛋仙人所在地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣圓喵的伊呂波老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼弄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候 就輪到我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有靈感了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡這樣 那裡那樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在御神杖神社。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是附近的神社 去那裡就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是老年人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡供奉著神杖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說誠心參拜的話 就能夠長壽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs40}（奈良是有個御神杖神社，有一顆相傳是神仙的手杖幻化而成的杉樹。）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 出乎意料的就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 快上去搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面 我叫四葉心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是仙人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 你是仙人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我只是普通的凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失...失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 剛才羞得都想挖個洞跳進去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到覺得一定就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飽了 繼續去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 再休息一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽曬得暖暖的 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡個午覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼連我都想睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 我說心彩啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要睡什麼時候！ X 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我的吐槽都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東奔西跑的肯定很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠我們自己去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找到蛋仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡有個屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是蛋仙人的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有光從裡面漏出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在 過不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 有個碗漂過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家乘上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻 嘿咻～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金光閃閃的蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無疑問就是他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 莫有疙瘩！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 塗塗他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋仙人就在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點大力敲開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在這裡喲～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的聲音是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老朽就是偉大的仙人愛心蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋仙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人就是蛋仙人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『來決勝負！蛋仙人』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與想像中的完全不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有仙人的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說跟我們有什麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒穿胖次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到是有穿兜襠布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這貨真是仙人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們見識一下仙人的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現吧觔斗雲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是放屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 當然沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是為了展示老朽也有調皮的一面的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 嚇尿了 還以為真要摔死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能問蛋仙人一些問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想問什麼 被選中的契約者 心彩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都可以問哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些提示的紙片 是蛋仙人留下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些假情報是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然騙人 太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒耍你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是正確的拼法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 老朽從昨天夜裡起 就一直在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只緣身在此山中 指的就是這回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獎勵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽已經下山了 過期了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來點好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定我改變主意 給你們點獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽烤的蛋糕真是太棒了（畢竟是Cure Rhythm...）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還算可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說蛋糕 愛心蛋界的可要美味個上千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？愛心蛋界 那是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那樣的地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像嘗嘗愛心蛋界的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快帶我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見習生是不能去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼要怎麼才能去到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要持續修煉 直到能夠獨當一面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是成長之後的愛心蛋 才能去到的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這正是愛心蛋界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟的愛心蛋能光明正大的在人類世界行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用躲躲藏藏的 也能為人類帶來幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 再也不用偷偷摸摸的躲到蛋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快點轉正 好吃的也能隨便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的志向也太小了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼愛心蛋界是怎麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是超級棒的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請再說的詳細一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不告訴你們～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然說偉大的仙人小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是事實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還不是沒給獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這小氣仙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 既然說到這份上了 就告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要贏過老朽再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏 比什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就比你們各自最善長的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管放馬過來 鵪鶉蛋們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在開始塗塗對蛋仙人的一場定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我四葉心彩擔當主持及裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽項目 高速甩屁屁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁屁甩的快的那一方獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 怎麼可能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備 開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 假的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋仙人 獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個挑戰者是美蘿莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡拉OK大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（好想聽愛生唱OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 與大家來相見！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰敲出了...小神仙！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現吧 大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現？個蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋仙人 獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一場是繞口令 連續三次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生麥子 小生抱歉 生的愛心蛋 X 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 比不過我 放棄了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 早就說完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來看證明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢速播放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生麥子 小生抱歉 生的愛心蛋 X 3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太扯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著是化妝大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是姬菈莉絲化妝的美蘿莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把美蘿莉的可愛之處都襯托了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是蛋仙人化妝的莎莎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害！閃閃發光的化妝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋仙人 獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後是拼圖大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋仙人 獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 最後一位挑戰者是吞撻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比誰吃披薩快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠你了 吞撻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就指望你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們愛心蛋全體的名譽就賭在你的胃口上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要贏啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的胃口怎麼可能會輸給老頭子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備 開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我太厲害了 嚇到動彈不得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 這種程度就可以了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋仙人 獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別小看仙人的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全敗給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 哈哈 哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白什麼是山外青山樓外樓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還有的練了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 難道這比賽是為了讓大家明白修煉的重要之處？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 的確是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒這想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就順勢而為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是果然還是很想知道愛心蛋界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成長起來 堂堂正正的去 就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 給你們這個 打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個難道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是獎勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就到聖誕節了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就送你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖誕節要辦很快樂的派對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有很多好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們誕生以來 第一個大節日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁屁！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰碰～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見習愛心蛋們 再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝蛋仙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的愛心蛋占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的幸運蛋是哪個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.63,0:24:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選中我的 肯定會是華麗的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常去的煙紙店遭遇危機了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危機是啥好吃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吃的...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.41,0:24:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為附近新開了古怪的零食店
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.06,0:24:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙紙店要倒閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就吃不到好吃的零食了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.33,0:24:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.11,0:24:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那是新的愛心蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.36,0:24:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集『在煙紙店砰砰砰！』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
